===Etymology===
From {{etyl|enm|en}} {{term|payen||lang=enm}} from {{etyl|fro|en}} {{term|paier||lang=fro}} from {{etyl|ML.}} ''[[pacare|pācāre]]'' "to settle, satisfy" from {{etyl|la|en}} {{term|pac|pacō|lang=la|to pacify}}. Displaced native {{enm}} ''[[yelden#Middle English|yelden, yielden]]'' "to pay" (from {{ang}} ''[[gieldan#Old English|ġieldan]]'' "to pay"), {{enm}} ''[[scotten#Middle English|schotten]]'' "to pay, make payment" (from {{ang}} ''[[gescot#Old English|scot, ġescot]]'' "payment").

